BarClock Title Bar Clock v4.20 <ASP> BarClock
is a handy utlity that makes use of the 
unused space in the title bar. Useful for 
time & date display, BarClock goes much 
further to include program launch icons, task
switch icons and a fully customizable 
display. BarClock also includes resource 
warnings, alarms, timers and a built in 
calendar!
